STATE v. CUPID No. COA04-137. North Carolina Court of Appeals. Filed September 20, 2005. Certification Date October 10, 2005. Appeal from Guilford (02CRS102982, 02CRS102985, 03CRS24126).

Case reported without published opinion. Motion for Appropriate Relief is allowed in part and denied in part. Case remanded for resentencing.
